---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="DIY Garage Cabinet Assembly — GlideLock"
  description="Klovo GlideLock assembly: panels lock together by hand, about 2-3 minutes per cabinet, full set in less than 1 hour. The only tool you'll need is a screwdriver for the back panel."
  keywords="DIY garage cabinet assembly, RTA garage cabinet, GlideLock, push-to-open garage cabinets, modular garage cabinets, ready to assemble garage cabinet kit"
>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Fast Assembly</span>
      <h1 class="page-h1">Flat box to<br/>finished in <em>3 minutes.</em></h1>
      <p class="page-lede">
        No cam locks. No Allen wrenches. Panels interlock by hand into a weight-bearing construction. One cabinet in about 2–3 minutes. A full set in less than 1 hour.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Video Section -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="page-video-card">
          <img
            src="/images/assembly/hands-pressing.png"
            alt="Klovo cabinet assembly demonstration"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <button
            type="button"
            data-video-open
            class="page-video-play"
            aria-label="Play assembly video"
          >
            <span class="page-video-play-circle">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="color: var(--ink); margin-left: 3px;">
                <polygon points="6,4 20,12 6,20" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="page-video-badge">
            <span class="page-video-badge-dot"></span>
            Watch · 0:41
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3 Steps -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--neutral);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span>
      <h2 class="h-section">Three steps.<br/><em>That's it.</em></h2>
      <div class="page-steps" style="margin-top: 48px; max-width: 640px;">
        <div class="page-step">
          <div class="page-step-num">1</div>
          <div class="page-step-body">
            <h3>Unbox the panels</h3>
            <p>Open the box and lay out the pre-drilled panels. Everything is labeled and arrives ready to build.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-step">
          <div class="page-step-num">2</div>
          <div class="page-step-body">
            <h3>Push and lock</h3>
            <p>Align the panels and push them together. The GlideLock connector system locks them into a secure, weight-bearing construction. Then drive a few screws through the back panel runners to secure it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-step">
          <div class="page-step-num">3</div>
          <div class="page-step-body">
            <h3>Done. Load it up.</h3>
            <p>Your cabinet holds 500 lbs and the box took about 2–3 minutes to build. Door, drawer, and hardware install is easy too.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Connector — Two-Column Split -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split" style="align-items: center;">
        <div class="split-media">
          <img
            src="/images/assembly/hands-garage.png"
            alt="Close-up of the Klovo connector system — panels pressing together"
            style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block; aspect-ratio:1/1; object-fit:cover;"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="split-text">
          <span class="eyebrow">The GlideLock Connector</span>
          <h2 class="h-section">Panels interlock.<br/><em>No tools for the box.</em></h2>
          <p style="font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 20px;">
            Most cabinet brands use cam locks, dowels, or screws that require tools and patience. Our GlideLock connector is different: panels push together and lock into a secure, weight-bearing construction.
          </p>
          <p style="font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 16px;">
            The only tool you'll need is a screwdriver to secure the back panel through the runners. That's it.
          </p>
          <ul class="page-tick-list" style="margin-top: 28px;">
            <li>
              <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
              Panels interlock into a secure construction — almost tool-free
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
              Push-to-open doors and drawers — no handles needed
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
              Disassembles just as easily — moves with you
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Table -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--neutral);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Comparison</span>
      <h2 class="h-section">Klovo vs.<br/><em>the old way.</em></h2>
      <div style="margin-top: 40px; overflow-x: auto;">
        <table class="page-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th></th>
              <th>Klovo</th>
              <th>Traditional</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Assembly Time</strong></td>
              <td><strong>2–3 min per box, &lt;1 hr per set</strong></td>
              <td>4+ hours</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Tools Required</strong></td>
              <td><strong>Screwdriver only</strong></td>
              <td>Drill, level, hardware</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Handles</strong></td>
              <td><strong>Push-to-open (none needed)</strong></td>
              <td>Hardware required</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Portable</strong></td>
              <td><strong>Yes — disassembles</strong></td>
              <td>Permanent install</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Band -->
  <section class="page-cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color: rgba(244,236,219,0.55);">See a Set</span>
      <h2 class="h-final">Find the set that fits<br/><em>your garage.</em></h2>
      <div class="page-cta-btns">
        <a href="/sets/" class="btn btn--primary">View sets &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/where-to-buy/" class="btn btn--ghost btn--ghost--dark">Find a retailer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Video Modal (Vimeo — portrait 9:16) -->
  <div
    id="video-modal"
    style="display:none; position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:200; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(15,10,4,0.92); backdrop-filter:blur(4px); padding:1rem;"
    role="dialog"
    aria-modal="true"
    aria-label="Assembly video"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <div style="position:relative; width:100%; max-width:min(90vw,45vh); margin:0 auto;">
      <button
        type="button"
        data-video-close
        aria-label="Close video"
        style="position:absolute; top:-3rem; right:0; background:none; border:0; cursor:pointer; color:#F4ECDB; line-height:1;"
      >
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18" />
          <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18" />
        </svg>
      </button>
      <div style="position:relative; background:#000; border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden; aspect-ratio:9/16; box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);">
        <div id="video-iframe-container" style="position:absolute; inset:0;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var modal = document.getElementById('video-modal');
      var container = document.getElementById('video-iframe-container');
      var openBtns = document.querySelectorAll('[data-video-open]');
      var closeBtns = document.querySelectorAll('[data-video-close]');
      var vimeoSrc = 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/1131081541?autoplay=1&title=0&byline=0&portrait=0&badge=0&autopause=0&player_id=0&app_id=58479';

      function openModal() {
        if (!modal || !container) return;
        container.innerHTML = '<iframe src="' + vimeoSrc + '" style="width:100%;height:100%;border:0;" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" title="Klovo Assembly Video"></iframe>';
        modal.style.display = 'flex';
        modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
        document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
      }

      function closeModal() {
        if (!modal || !container) return;
        modal.style.display = 'none';
        modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
        container.innerHTML = '';
        document.body.style.overflow = '';
      }

      openBtns.forEach(function (b) { b.addEventListener('click', openModal); });
      closeBtns.forEach(function (b) { b.addEventListener('click', closeModal); });
      if (modal) {
        modal.addEventListener('click', function (e) { if (e.target === modal) closeModal(); });
      }
      document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
        if (e.key === 'Escape' && modal && modal.style.display !== 'none') closeModal();
      });
    })();
  </script>

</PageLayout>
